{"word":"H5668 - עָבוּר - ʻâbûwr - aw-boor' - Because of","slug":"H5668","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָבוּר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻâbûwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-boor'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Because of"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D1;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E2;&#x05D1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E8; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;bu&#x0302;r  &#x201B;a&#x0302;bu&#x0302;r</b> - <i>aw-boor', aw-boor'</i><p/>Passive participle of <a href=\"#/H5674\">H5674</a>; properly <i>crossed</i>, that is, (abstractly) <i>transit</i>; used only adverbially on <i>account</i> of, in <i>order</i> that: - because of, for (. . . &lsquo;s sake), (intent) that, to."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4569\">H4569</a>, <a href=\"#/H5669\">H5669</a>, <a href=\"#/H5674\">H5674</a>, <a href=\"#/H5676\">H5676</a>, <a href=\"#/H5677\">H5677</a>, <a href=\"#/H5678\">H5678</a>, <a href=\"#/H5679\">H5679</a>, <a href=\"#/H5680\">H5680</a>, <a href=\"#/H5681\">H5681</a>, <a href=\"#/H5682\">H5682</a>, <a href=\"#/H5683\">H5683</a>, <a href=\"#/H5684\">H5684</a>"}]}